{"questionId":"12217","questionHtml":"<p>Show that&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a + d = 1\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>Attempting to find <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {{a^2} + bc}&amp;{ab + bd} \\\\   {ac + cd}&amp;{bc + {d^2}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mi>d</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mi>d</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>d</mi>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span><em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\\left( {a + d} \\right) = b\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span> or&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"c\\left( {a + d} \\right) = c\">\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n</math></span><em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>Hence&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a + d = 1\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;(as&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b \\ne 0\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span> or <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"c \\ne 0\">\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>AG&nbsp; N0</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12217","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.22a.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Show that a + d = 1 .","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}